  <class_name>SetRoofInsulation</class_name>
  <display_name>Set Roof Insulation (Target Assembly R)</display_name>
  <description>Creates/assigns a simple roof construction (membrane + insulation + roof board) to all outdoor RoofCeiling surfaces, sizing insulation to hit a target assembly R-value (IP).</description>
  <modeler_description>Targets whole-assembly R by subtracting fixed layer RSI from target RSI to determine insulation thickness. Reuses objects by name, clamps thickness, reports achieved R.</modeler_description>
